how to use drvopt optimizer:

1) compile set of ppd files into one optimized drv
   
	drvopt -d /hp -o hp.drv

2) compress received .drv file by gzip:
	
	gzip hp.drv


how to use getdrv extractor:

1) extract requred driver by model name:

	getdrv -i stripped.drv -r <modelname>

or

extract required driver by Product attribute:

	getdrv -p <product> -i hp.drv